{"data": [{"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "0_1773982024.867154", "card_id": "Q_2018050979702989965", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 200}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "小米新一代 SU7 发布，王传福、李想、何小鹏纷纷到场助阵，怎样解读？小米汽车在行业内有怎样的影响力？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "3 月 19 日晚，小米汽车召开新一代 SU7 发布会，小米集团董事长雷军亮相发布会。 直播画面显示，发布会现场比亚迪集团董事长兼总裁王传福、理想汽车 CEO 李想、小鹏汽车董事长、 CEO 何小鹏等都有亮相。雷军对于他们的到来多次表示感谢。 据悉，宇树科技创始人王兴兴也携宇树机器人到现场为新一代 SU7 站台。 小米汽车召开新一代 SU7 发布会，雷军多次道谢，王兴兴、何小鹏等到场助阵"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-d020168adde744f75e15d978b05be1ab_720w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "695 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2018050979702989965"}}, "attached_info": "CkoIzL30/b/xjN9JEAMaCTExODgyMTE0MCDPxO/NBjAAOJcDQAByEzIwMTgwNTA5Nzk3MDI5ODk5NjV4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "1_1773982024.868513", "card_id": "Q_2017860793417356112", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 208}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何看待内存条价格崩了？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "目前我听说是从 3500 掉到了 2700。有没有懂的朋友？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-3cdb4310558e09d207a8ebbbaac679b5_1440w.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "645 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2017860793417356112"}}, "attached_info": "CkoIzL30/b/xjN9JEAMaCTExODgxMTM2OCCv4uzNBjAAONMDQAFyEzIwMTc4NjA3OTM0MTczNTYxMTJ4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "2_1773982024.869015", "card_id": "