 "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2018114384203924458"}}, "attached_info": "CkoIzL30/b/xjN9JEAMaCTExODgyNDA1NCDbuvDNBjAAOJMCQApyEzIwMTgxMTQzODQyMDM5MjQ0NTh4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "11_1773982024.875533", "card_id": "Q_2017891290054943068", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 333}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "小米 SU7 应网友呼声官宣舒淇为代言人，从品牌营销角度如何评价这一做法？会给品牌带来哪些变化？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "3 月 19 日，小米汽车官方正式宣布演员、导演舒淇出任小米汽车品牌代言人，这是继 3 月 17 日官宣苏炳添后，小米汽车在三天内公布的第二位品牌代言人。 小米汽车官方发文称：「从镜头前，到镜头后。她，始终以从容的姿态，保持自己的节奏，不断走向新的世界。今天，她又解锁了一个新角色，小米汽车品牌代言人。不仅因为，她非常喜爱第一代 SU7 的乘坐体验。更因为，我们都拥有，从容驾驭每一程的底气。」 小米汽车官宣舒淇为第二位代言人，新一代 SU7 今晚正式上市 _ 腾讯新闻"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-d863e532ae3d823f6b299fc8c6c6cd57.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "100 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2017891290054943068"}}, "attached_info": "CkoIzL30/b/xjN9JEAMaCTExODgxMjMxMiCWm+3NBjAAONgDQAtyEzIwMTc4OTEyOTAwNTQ5NDMwNjh4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "12_1773982024.876456", "card_id": "Q_2018140366411408037", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 22}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何评价《一人之下》漫画第 756（806）话？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "「致死」"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-04615bf8b9265e812e6350fdaffa8d38_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "98 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2018140366411408037"}}, "attached_info": "CkkIzL30/b/xjN9JEAMaCTEx